Q3.Mention some of the core benefits of DevOps?
1. It act as bridge between dev teams, ops team, and testing team has been erased which in turn helps in business to become more responsive and inclined towards the business and market conditions.    
2. It brings innovation to the new business using feedback formula that will help in creating products with creativity and efficiently which will provide happy customers.
3. In DevOps With continuous integration and deployment being the core of the DevOps process that helps bring the product faster into market.
4.The ability of an organization to be agile in their adoption and implementation plays a vital role in bringing about transformation within a business.
